craft
------------------------------------------
Minecraft clone for Windows, Mac OS X and Linux. Just a few thousand lines of
C using modern OpenGL (shaders). Online multiplayer support is included using
a Python-based server.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libGLEW2.1-2.1.0-1
  libcurl4-8.17.0-1
  libglfw3-3.4-1bl2
  liblodepng0-0+git20250402-1bl1
  libsqlite3_0-3.49.1-1
  libtinycthread1-1.2+git20161001-1bl2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-4.1.3-1
  cygport-0.37.5-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libGLEW-devel-2.1.0-1
  libcurl-devel-8.17.0-1
  libglfw-devel-3.4-1bl2
  liblodepng-devel-0+git20250402-1bl1
  libsqlite3-devel-3.49.1-1
  libtinycthread-devel-1.2+git20161001-1bl2
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/fogleman/Craft

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/fogleman/Craft/archive/v1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack craft-1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./craft-1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/craft-1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/craft-1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(craft)
  /usr/bin/craft.exe
  /usr/lib/craft/builder.py
  /usr/lib/craft/server.py
  /usr/lib/craft/world.py
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/block_fragment.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/block_vertex.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/line_fragment.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/line_vertex.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/sky_fragment.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/sky_vertex.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/text_fragment.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/shaders/text_vertex.glsl
  /usr/share/craft/textures/font.png
  /usr/share/craft/textures/sign.png
  /usr/share/craft/textures/sky.png
  /usr/share/craft/textures/texture.png
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/craft.README
  /usr/share/doc/craft/LICENSE.md
  /usr/share/doc/craft/README.md

